  <brief_title>Triclosan Coated Suture Wound Closure for Peripheral Vascular Surgery: a Prospective Multicenter Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Triclosan Coated Suture Wound Closure for Peripheral Vascular Surgery: a Prospective Multicenter Study</official_title>
