  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective randomized multicenter study which purpose is to determine whether
      triclosan-coated sutures for wound closure after lower limb vascular surgery would reduce the
      incidence of surgical wound infections.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
